title: Introducing: DUNES
body:
Digging the early 00’s pop vibes coming from this debut offering from New Zealand duo **DUNES**.

Sisters Jamie and Tess McDell channel some serious Charli XCX grooves on the irresistibly sugary sweet _Girlfriends and Boyfriends_. Check it out below.

Like this? Follow our [On Repeat Playlist](https://open.spotify.com/user/crackintheroad/playlist/1UB6gJIZpmiO0H2zmSbg02) for a handpicked selection of the very best in new music; updated weekly.
